    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>反游戏：</strong></h2>No Fair Play (没有公平竞争) 是一款允许玩家通过各种手段击败对手的多人游戏。<br>对方队员是个优秀的盘球手？瞄准他的腿部！打、推、抢、抓...一切都由你决定，如何获得优势。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/77f84fa38ca6dca6d908cad9e44e01f2.poster.avif?t=1733990004\" width=552 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/77f84fa38ca6dca6d908cad9e44e01f2.webm?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/77f84fa38ca6dca6d908cad9e44e01f2.mp4?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多人游戏和机器人：</strong></h2>开始时使用机器人，结束时与真实玩家一同游戏。您可以允许其他玩家加入您的游戏并替换机器人。如果有人退出游戏或断开连接，机器人将立即接替他的位置。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>基于物理：</strong></h2>布娃娃、控制球、球员之间的互动... 物理给玩家提供更多意外情况下的乐趣机会。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/53b0244df58779ae23c0bd94c8472ffd.poster.avif?t=1733990004\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/53b0244df58779ae23c0bd94c8472ffd.webm?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/53b0244df58779ae23c0bd94c8472ffd.mp4?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直观的游戏玩法：</strong></h2>简单的控制和规则，球会飞向您瞄准的位置，射击角度会自动计算。但是简单的游戏玩法并不意味着限制。还有许多需要技巧的高级机制。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/946abfe919472ed7480d12a517cd1539.poster.avif?t=1733990004\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/946abfe919472ed7480d12a517cd1539.webm?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/946abfe919472ed7480d12a517cd1539.mp4?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>跑酷机制：</strong></h2>跑酷地图和跑酷游戏模式，为那些想要更多的挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/232f693cd19ddc6b6a5cb416616da92f.poster.avif?t=1733990004\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/232f693cd19ddc6b6a5cb416616da92f.webm?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/232f693cd19ddc6b6a5cb416616da92f.mp4?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色定制：</strong></h2>选择发型、服装、颜色，加入到球场上。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/73b43ff5fd8e55ea31ea7b50449622b5.poster.avif?t=1733990004\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/73b43ff5fd8e55ea31ea7b50449622b5.webm?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1771180/extras/73b43ff5fd8e55ea31ea7b50449622b5.mp4?t=1733990004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>第一人称视角和VR：</strong></h2>您可以使用VR头戴式耳机或不使用头戴式耳机的第一人称视角进行游戏。<br>注意：需要一个带有2个摇杆的游戏手柄。",
